threatSourceDTO Data Type

Namespace
(Default)
Properties
name data type type namespace min/max occurs description
custom boolean element 1/1 Indicates if the threat source is a custom (non-system) threat source
description string element 0/1 Brief description of the threat source
enabled boolean element 1/1 Indicates if the threat source is enabled (true) for this org
id int element 1/1 The threat source's id
license string element 0/1 Returns the API license for this threat source
name string element 0/1 The threat source's display name
prompt_license boolean element 1/1 True if the license must be agreed to before this threat source can be enabled
properties (custom) element 0/1 The threat source's properties
tos threatSourceTosDTO element 0/1 An object describing the terms of service data that need to be collected before this threat service can be turned on
tos_agreement_date dateTime element 0/1 The date on which the terms of service for this threat service was agreed to

Example

<threatSourceDTO>
  <id>...</id>
  <name>...</name>
  <description>...</description>
  <enabled>...</enabled>
  <custom>...</custom>
  <tos_agreement_date>...</tos_agreement_date>
  <prompt_license>...</prompt_license>
  <license>...</license>
  <properties>...</properties>
  <tos>
    <tos_url>...</tos_url>
    <fields>
      <type>...</type>
      <id>...</id>
      <label>...</label>
      <value>...</value>
    </fields>
  </tos>
</threatSourceDTO>
